WEBVTT

00:00:02.200 --> 00:00:06.640 line:13 position:50% align:center size:65%
Many side effects are short-lived and are easily managed at home. Some however,

00:00:06.640 --> 00:00:10.880 line:13 position:50% align:center size:65%
may last longer or occur weeks or months 
after your last dose of treatment.

00:00:11.320 --> 00:00:14.640 line:13 position:50% align:center size:65%
Remember it is important to keep your healthcare team informed.

00:00:15.160 --> 00:00:19.920 line:13 position:50% align:center size:65%
The patient alert card contains important 
safety information about your Avelumab

00:00:20.160 --> 00:00:23.400 line:13 position:50% align:center size:65%
treatment. Keep this card with you during your treatment,

00:00:23.600 --> 00:00:26.280 line:13 position:50% align:center size:65%
and for three months after your last treatment,

00:00:26.640 --> 00:00:30.120 line:13 position:50% align:center size:65%
and always show it to any healthcare professional 
involved in your treatment.

